org.springframework.messaging.converter

接口 ContentTypeResolver

  • 所有已知实现类:
    DefaultContentTypeResolver
    函数接口:
    这是一个函数接口, 因此可用作 lambda 表达式或方法引用的赋值目标。

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface ContentTypeResolver
    Resolve the content type for a message.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.0
    作者:
    Rossen Stoyanchev

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      MimeType resolve(MessageHeaders headers)
      Determine the MimeType of a message from the given MessageHeaders.

    • 方法详细资料

      • resolve

        @Nullable
MimeType resolve(@Nullable
                            MessageHeaders headers)
                     throws InvalidMimeTypeException
        Determine the MimeType of a message from the given MessageHeaders.
        参数:
        headers - the headers to use for the resolution
        返回:
        the resolved MimeType, or null if none found
        抛出:
        InvalidMimeTypeException - if the content type is a String that cannot be parsed
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if there is a content type but its type is unknown
